
# 🩺 Diabetes Detection System

A Machine Learning-based web application that predicts whether a person is diabetic or not based on medical input parameters. The system uses trained models to provide accurate and fast predictions.

---

## 📌 Features

- 🔍 Predicts diabetes based on user input
- 📊 Uses Machine Learning algorithms
- 🖥️ Simple and user-friendly interface
- ⚡ Fast and accurate predictions
- 📈 Data preprocessing and model training included

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Python
- Pandas, NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib / Seaborn (for visualization)
- Flask (for web app, if used)
- HTML, CSS (for frontend)

---

## 📂 Project Structure
Diabetes_Detection_Project/
│
├── app.py # Flask application (if applicable)
├── model.py # ML model training script
├── diabetes.csv # Dataset
├── templates/ # HTML files
├── static/ # CSS/JS files
├── model.pkl # Saved trained model
├── requirements.txt # Dependencies
└── README.md


---

